	Submitted: Fabrice Fontaine ( ffontaine ) - 2012-03-05 12:33:59 PST

	Fp is not closed when an error is raised on membuffer_append or
	sock_read.

2012-03-05 Fabrice Fontaine <fabrice.fontaine(at)orange.com>

