	Submitted: Fabrice Fontaine ( ffontaine ) - 2012-02-28 04:27:54 PST

	ixmlFreeDOMString(ActNodeName); is called twice if
	ixmlParseBufferEx(ActNodeName, RespNode); does not return IXML_SUCCESS.

