	* gena_subscribe(): Fix for IPV6 ULA/GUA issues.
	
	Patch submitted by Ronan Menard.

2010-08-21 Marcelo Jimenez <mroberto(at)users.sourceforge.net>
	* SOCKET ssdpSock6UlaGua: created variable for later use.
	
